Last Broadcast Date: Thu 14 Jun 2012
The Peruvian police officer who survived 17 days in the jungle after being shot in a gun battle with Shining Path rebels. Matthew talks to him from his hospital bed. Also, the former British soldier who grew to love Afghanistan - and set out with his young family to start a business in a remote part of the country. Show less